00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:54,630
it's the first time she's seen

296
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:56,720
someone contradict His Highness like that.

297
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,030
You're really something.

298
00:16:58,030 --> 00:16:59,450
I just spoke my mind.

299
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:00,270
So what?

300
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:03,430
Worst case, he'd chop off my head

301
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:05,609
and find you a new consort.

302
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,880
Who wants that?

303
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:09,680
His Highness said

304
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,920
if you stay here,

305
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:13,750
he will keep you safe.

306
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:15,920
I...

307
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,589
I can stay too.

308
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,170
If not for you, Chang Yu'er,

309
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:27,530
I'd be dead ten times over.

310
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:32,150
If I were a free man,

311
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,630
I'd stay here on the grasslands.

312
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,640
Riding horses and herding sheep

313
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,480
every day.

314
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:40,610
That would be nice.

315
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,000
But I'm not.

316
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:49,030
What's the big deal?

317
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,830
First time seeing you like this.

318
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,630
You're not even afraid of death,

319
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:54,680
yet you're beating around the bush.

320
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:56,140
It's just exile, isn't it?

321
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:59,110
The imperial court hasn't caught you.

322
00:17:59,110 --> 00:18:00,480
Let's say...

323
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,550
Let's say...

324
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,960
I caught you.

325
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,590
You, the princess,

326
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,770
are a real princess.

327
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:13,200
But I, the consort,

328
00:18:14,550 --> 00:18:15,750
am a fake.

329
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,970
I am engaged back home.

330
