Youâ€¦

331
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,680
You never mentioned that.

332
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,570
Before,

333
00:18:43,710 --> 00:18:45,320
I told you about my father.

334
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,790
We were very poor then.

335
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,800
Couldn't afford school.

336
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:51,750
The village schoolteacher,

337
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:52,800
Mr. Bai,

338
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:53,790
took pity on me

339
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:56,440
and taught me to read for free.

340
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,960
He had a daughter

341
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:01,000
named Bai Yimei.

342
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:03,030
Before I went to the capital for exams,

343
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:04,690
we exchanged betrothal gifts

344
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,580
and were officially engaged.

345
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,480
I planned that after the exams,

346
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,320
I'd go back and marry her.

347
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:16,200
So...

348
00:19:18,110 --> 00:19:19,240
so where is she now?

349
00:19:21,210 --> 00:19:21,790
Now?

350
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:25,760
I don't know.

351
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,520
I have no idea.

352
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:44,840
Anyway,

353
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,400
I think

354
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,020
since we have

355
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:50,070
faced death together,

356
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,480
I owe you the truth.

357
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:59,130
I am an exile,

358
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,270
and I am engaged.

359
00:20:02,170 --> 00:20:03,370
I'm not worthy of you.

360
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:19,960
I think...

361
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:25,580
I've really had too much to drink.

362
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,750
Wearing this outfit...

363
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,600
made me forget reality.

364
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:35,260
This whole thing
about the princess and her consort...

365
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:37,610
was just play-acting.

366
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,860
Your Highness.

367
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,400
Don't walk further.

368
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,420
Alright.

369
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,920
Get up, sweetie.

370
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:53,130
Your Highness.

371
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,830
I am so fond of this girl.

372
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,880
You don't care for gold or jewels,

373
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,640
so I'm giving you this jade pendant.

374
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,960
If one day

375
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,350
you are in trouble,

376
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:10,520
send someone

377
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:12,060
to bring this pendant to me.

378
00:22:12,300 --> 00:22:13,580
No matter how far,

379
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:16,630
Horqin warriors will come

380
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,970
to solve your problems.

381
00:22:20,330 --> 00:22:22,380
Especially the problem next to you.

382
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,560
I can see that this guy

383
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,350
doesn't truly want to marry you.

384
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,330
I don't want him anyway.

385
00:22:33,450 --> 00:22:35,380
You really won't stay?

386
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:39,080
No matter what mistake you made,

387
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:41,240
I'd protect you.

388
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:45,930
Thank you for your great kindness.

389
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:48,190
But I miss my home dearly.

390
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,250
My elderly mother is there.

391
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,570
I cannot travel far.

392
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,330
The matter with Hanlong

393
00:22:54,590 --> 00:22:55,930
has been taken care of.

394
00:22:56,790 --> 00:22:58,070
You suffered a great injustice

395
00:22:58,070 --> 00:22:59,670
during your visit this time.

396
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:01,270
Thank you, Your Highness.

397
00:23:01,270 --> 00:23:03,150
Thank you for your hospitality.

398
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:04,720
We shall meet again.

399
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,240
Good.

400
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:06,720
Until we meet again.

401
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:08,160
Please.

402
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,350
Take care.

403
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:22,680
Take care, sweetie.

404
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,570
Take care, sweetie.

405
00:23:29,030 --> 00:23:29,960
Let's depart.

406
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:45,510
[Li Wantang's Mansion in the capital]

407
00:23:45,510 --> 00:23:47,160
Here are the land deeds

408
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:48,610
and the reserve funds.

409
00:23:49,270 --> 00:23:50,800
Keep the silver cash on you.

410
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:53,900
You'll manage
the Pingyao draft bank yourself.

411
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,530
Don't worry about that.

412
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,840
The banking business

413
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,730
relies on financial strength.

414
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:00,400
Surely the Li family's wealth

415
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,750
can match theirs.

416
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:03,560
It'd be ridiculous otherwise.

417
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,090
You can't say that.

418
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,390
In business,

419
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:09,400
unity is the most important thing.

420
00:24:10,590 --> 00:24:12,070
I hear the Shanxi merchants

421
00:24:12,070 --> 00:24:13,330
are extremely united.

422
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,200
That's crucial.

423
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,030
Master.

424
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,540
There is something

425
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,530
I don't know if I should say.

426
00:24:22,070 --> 00:24:22,600
Go ahead.

427
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,170
Some in the family say

428
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:27,830
investing so much

429
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:29,990
to open a draft bank in Shanxi

430
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:32,280
might not be worth the risk.

431
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,740
Is it written that

432
00:24:37,830 --> 00:24:39,160
only Shanxi people

433
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,930
are allowed to run draft banks?

434
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:44,830
That is exactly what I told them.

435
00:24:44,830 --> 00:24:45,750
I'm just worried that you are

436
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:47,880
getting too close to the southerners.

437
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:49,970
Is it too risky?

438
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:51,370
I have my plans.

439
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:57,210
Father.

440
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,040
I've packed everything.

441
00:24:59,070 --> 00:24:59,790
Good.

442
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,900
Before you go,

443
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,880
I have a few words for you.

444
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,160
I'm all ears.

445
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:10,000
This is our first time

446
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:11,640
entering the lion's den in Shanxi

447
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,920
to compete for our share.

448
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,960
Who knows how many people

449
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,420
are waiting to see us fail.

450
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,120
Do not be careless.

451
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:19,400
Yes. I certainly won't

452
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:21,040
disgrace the Li family name.

453
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,710
What name do we have?

454
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,120
Business is like war.

455
00:25:27,270 --> 00:25:29,200
You just have to fight a few battles.

456
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,460
Don't be arrogant because of our wealth.

457
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:34,670
And don't secretly look down on others.

458
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:37,130
That's a land full of rich merchants.

459
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:39,710
Learn and ask questions
when you get there.

460
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:40,680
Sure.

461
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,700
Pawnshops and banks

462
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,960
run on a cycle of inflow and outflow.

463
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,520
Money shouldn't flow too fast,

464
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,520
nor too slow.

465
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:51,830
The stakes involved...

466
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:57,160
Enough.

467
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:58,720
When you do it yourself there,

468
00:25:58,720 --> 00:25:59,920
you will understand.

469
00:26:00,790 --> 00:26:02,150
I'm telling you now.

470
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,400
You are the vanguard this time.

471
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:06,390
If you fail, I will step in.

472
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:07,890
But don't blame me then

473
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,360
if I show you no mercy.

474
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,720
Understood!

475
00:26:16,220 --> 00:26:20,900
[Shanxi]

476
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:41,640
You have to leave after all.

477
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,450
I'm a fugitive.

478
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:45,370
I have no right to say such things.

479
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,620
Don't overthink it.

480
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:49,240
Go back and take care of your father.

481
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,460
Will...

482
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:58,920
Will you...

483
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,000
w-will you come see me?

484
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:03,850
I mean...

485
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,280
after you marry Miss Bai.

486
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,480
I hope so.

487
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,270
I have an elderly mother

488
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:16,400
and a younger brother at home.

489
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,440
Often in my dreams,

490
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,300
I think of them.

491
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:21,200
I've burdened them all these years.

492
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:23,030
If my family

493
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:25,660
suffers any more misfortune,

494
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:27,400
I don't know if Heaven

495
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,600
will ever forgive me.

496
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:32,320
You haven't wronged anyone.

497
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,050
Take care.

498
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:50,720
Fugitive Gu Pingyuan!

499
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:52,110
Dismount and surrender!

500
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,680
Chang Si is to be arrested as well.

501
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,790
Harboring a fugitive

502
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:56,250
carries the same penalty!

503
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,980
Fugitive Gu Pingyuan!

504
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,400
Dismount and surrender!

505
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,920
Chang Si is to be arrested as well.

506
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,030
Harboring a fugitive

507
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:03,490
carries the same penalty!

508
00:28:28,030 --> 00:28:28,590
Master,

509
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,480
the county magistrate is here.

510
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,080
Let me ask you something.

511
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,710
These pawnshop accounts...

512
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:39,200
How were they kept?

513
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:40,350
Who kept them?

514
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,880
They rushed to finish them
before the Spring Festival.

515
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:45,610
The head and second managers
have reviewed them.

516
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:50,270
So small?

517
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:52,550
So thin?

518
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:56,480
The pawnshop accounts
for the past five years

519
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:58,790
are getting increasingly simplified.

520
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:03,040
Do they

521
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:05,400
have no respect for me?

522
00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:09,130
The two managers are getting old.

523
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,140
They lack energy.

524
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,720
Is it a lack of energy?

525
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:14,830
I think they just

526
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:17,160
don't respect me!

527
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,720
Isn't it just because

528
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:26,010
I have no son?

529
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:29,110
Because I have no heir?

530
00:29:36,250 --> 00:29:38,070
[Magistrate of Pingyao]

531
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:42,660
[Auspicious Clouds]

532
00:29:42,660 --> 00:29:45,000
I've been waiting for you for ages.

533
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,560
Your Worship, you're here.

534
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,480
Forgive me for not greeting you sooner.

535
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,480
What happened

536
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:52,960
with Chang Si caused quite a stir.

537
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:54,510
I can't suppress it anymore.

538
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:56,660
I can't explain it to my superiors.

539
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:59,690
Who do you need to explain it to?

540
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:02,880
The prefecture has its governor;
the circuit has its intendant.

541
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:05,570
A lowly seventh-rank official like me

542
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,440
has to report to them.

543
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:08,720
Besides,

544
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:12,190
the convict with Chang Si

545
00:30:12,790 --> 00:30:14,080
is an exile

546
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:16,460
who escaped from Ningguta.

547
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:19,000
Handing him over

548
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,200
would earn us major credit.

549
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:24,640
